      "rationale": "Three-level GCI completed on 4.1 M / 9.8 M / 22.4 M meshes. Apparent order p = 1.87 (formal order 2.0, within 7%). Fine-grid GCI for NIH = 3.9% < 5% threshold. Required and achieved levels both 4; criterion met."
