      "rationale": "Mean absolute error 12.3%; u_val computed per ASME V&V 20 = 13.8% including experimental scatter. All predictions within 95% CI. Metric marginally within 15% bound but combined uncertainty budget does not fully account for model-form error. Achieved level 3 vs required level 4."
