      "acceptanceCriteria": "Documented simulation workflow with peer-reviewed setup checklist; independent analyst reproduction of at least one operating point.",
      "rationale": "Simulation workflow documented in internal SOP. No independent analyst reproduction performed. Setup checklist not peer-reviewed externally. Significant gap: achieved level 2 vs required level 4 represents the largest single credibility shortfall in this assessment."
