      "acceptanceCriteria": "Turbulence model and hemolysis damage model selected based on published benchmark comparisons; model-form uncertainty quantified and included in total uncertainty budget.",
      "rationale": "k-ω SST turbulence model selected based on FDA critical path benchmark. Power-law Giersiepen-Wurzinger hemolysis model used; known to over-predict NIH at low shear rates. Model-form uncertainty estimated qualitatively but not formally included in u_val. Achieved level 3 vs required level 5 — largest model-form gap in the assessment."
    },
