      "acceptanceCriteria": "Minimum of three independent experimental replicates per operating point; inter-laboratory reproducibility demonstrated for at least one operating condition.",
      "rationale": "Three replicates performed per operating point within a single laboratory. No inter-laboratory reproducibility data available. Experimental scatter (CV = 11%) within acceptable range but single-laboratory limitation reduces confidence. Achieved level 3 vs required level 4."
